疫情期间，没口罩的硬核网友是怎样出门的？。
During epidemic period, do not mask hard core netizen how to go out?
地球人研究报告。
Earthman Study Report.
趣闻。
Interesting news.
※文中涉及案例均为“反面教材”，切勿模仿。
vt. no, not, never, never, seldom, little, little, hardly, little, little, little, little
特殊时期，请大家不要存在侥幸心理，一定要规范佩戴口罩。
Special period, please do not exist, we must standardize wearing masks.
。
.
大家这几天还好吗？。
How are you guys these days?
在疫情态势依然紧张的当下，社长最近一直积极响应号召龟缩在家，默默地 享受 承受着闲出屁来的日子，不出门给大伙添乱。
At a time when the epidemic is still tense, the president has been actively responding to the call to stay at home, quietly enjoying the idle days, do not go out to add chaos to the public.
。
.
但与此同时，也能见到很多小伙伴愈发耐不住内心的躁动，急于恢复春节期间本该进行的娱乐活动，顶风作案：。
But at the same time, can also see many small partners more impatient inner restlessness, eager to resume the Spring Festival should be held during the entertainment, the wind committed:.
这种行为当然是不提倡的。
Such behaviour is certainly not advocated.
虽然看起来武装严密，但集聚性的活动本身就会大大加重大家的感染风险。
Although it may seem heavily armed, concentrated activity itself can greatly increase the risk of infection for everyone.
与威胁自身安全相比，一时娱乐的代价显然得不偿失。
The cost of a moment's entertainment is clearly less than the cost of threatening one's own safety.
。
.
不过，不得不出门的情况也确实存在。
However, it is also true that people have to leave their homes.
但问题在于，大伙的口罩余粮已经渐渐捉襟见肘，这对许多家庭说确实成了一个麻烦事。
The problem, however, is that the surplus supply of masks is already running out, which is a real nuisance for many families.
。
.
即便各地的口罩生产厂商已经在加班加点地生产，口罩恢复正常供应也指日可待，但依然有居民越来越按捺不住出门的欲望，以至于——。
Even as mask makers around the world are already working overtime and supplies are expected to return to normal, residents are increasingly tempted to go out.
一些群众“机灵”的小脑瓜，终究还是不可避免地运转起来了：。
Some of the "clever" masses of the small head, after all, or the inevitable operation of up:.
其实，面对没有口罩的情况，我们能猜到人们会寻找出一些看起来合理的替代方案。
In fact, in the face of the absence of masks, we can guess that people will look for some reasonable alternative.
比如把高领毛衣进一步提高：。
Take a turtleneck sweater and raise it further.
比如翻出自己各种压箱底的“护具”：。
For example, turn out the bottom of their various "protective gear":.
这些办法虽然并不靠谱，多少还在常人的思考范围之内。
Although these methods are not reliable, more or less within the scope of ordinary people's thinking.
。
.
但是你也知道的，中国这片土地上，群众的才智总是让人摸不着范围上限。
But as you know, China is a land where the intellect of the masses is always beyond reach.
简单对大伙最近捣鼓出的那些神奇的口罩替代方案进行一下归类，主要能分出以下三种——。
Simple to everyone recently tampered with those magic mask replacement options for classification, can be divided into the following three -.
手工达人。
Artificial daredevil.
对于对自己动手能力有足够自信的大哥们来说，世间万物都是相通的。
For older brothers who have enough confidence in their own hands, everything in the world is the same.
没有口罩？绝对耽误不了办事——他们能研究出一万种替代方案。
No masks? Absolutely no delay - they can develop 10,000 alternatives.
。
.
靠不靠谱放一边，据我所知至少这种拿柚子做口罩的已经不是第一次出现了：。
It's not the first time I've seen such a grapefruit mask, but it's not the first time I've seen one.
但是这次，也不知道是不是因为大伙的时间过于充裕，水果外壳做口罩的流派已经蔓延到螃蟹了：。
But this time, I do not know whether the time is too abundant, the fruit shell mask school has spread to crabs:.
另一边，这种纯净水桶套头的策略本已不算不稀奇：。
On the other hand, this pure bucket hedging strategy is not uncommon:
但还是因为这次病毒的威慑力，而衍生出了进阶版的解决方案：。
But because of the deterrent power of this virus, and derived from an advanced version of the solution:.
如果你不怕让自己刚淘换GUCCI西服掉价，也不用追求那么高的制造工艺，只要能将自己的头部团团围住形成自闭空间，材料美观不美观，完全可以不是重点。
If you're not afraid to let yourself just panned out of a GUCCI suit, or pursue that high manufacturing process, as long as you can wrap your head around to form a self-contained space, the material is beautiful, can not be the focus.
。
.
但这类办法唯一的问题就是，这肺病还没等得上，咱就率先呼吸困难了：。
But the only problem with this method is that the lung disease is not yet ready, and we are the first to breathe.
反正大哥们也不在乎，他们知道，在这紧张的非常时期，能够信任的人只有自己。
In any case, the big brothers do not care, they know that in this tense emergency, can trust only their own people.
。
.
善假于物。
Good in goods.
这会儿的许多市场商店，都因为预防疫情的进一步扩散而要求入场者必须佩戴口罩。
Many market stores these days require people to wear masks in case the epidemic spreads further.
。
.
但如果不让通行的原因仅仅是“没戴口罩”的话，这点障碍可拦不住那些小机灵鬼们：。
But if the reason for not allowing access is simply "not wearing a mask," this barrier won't stop the nimble.
不敢想象，敢于这么做的小伙子究竟要靠什么样的心理素质才能躲过店员异样的眼神。
I can't imagine what kind of psychological quality a young man would rely on to avoid the strange eyes of a shop assistant.
。
.
但仔细想想，能耍出类似操作的朋友，早就不会在乎店员和周遭人们的眼神了。
But on second thought, a friend who can do something like that won't care about the shop assistants or the people around them.
相比之下，他们更喜欢也更善于做的事，是在日常生活中寻找可能性。
By contrast, what they prefer and are better able to do is to look for possibilities in their daily lives.
尤其是能发掘出那些生活中本应深藏不漏的物品的额外价值。
In particular, it uncovers the added value of things that should be hidden in our lives.
。
.
被挖掘出额外价值的还有这个……。
And this... has been unearthed for added value.
和这个……。
And this...
（咱就想知道宁这到底是什么牌子的，能如此透气？）。
I just want to know what brand this is, so breathable?
以及拿出泡面盒子冲锋陷阵的大爷。
And the man who took out the bubble-noodle box.
只是大爷，咱这玩意除了能让自己喘不上气来，真的没法防细菌（jǔn）。
It's just, Grandpa, we can't really protect ourselves from germs (j same conditions as n) except that we can't breathe.
。
.
走火入魔。
Got into trouble.
我知道，我们需要给到病毒足够的尊重，但总还是觉得一些朋友的防护手段有些夸张了。
I know we need to treat the virus with enough respect, but I still think some of my friends' defenses are exaggerated.
。
.
他们除了佩戴标准的口罩外，往往还自创了额外的防护手段，从经典的油瓶罐子：。
In addition to wearing standard masks, they often create their own additional protective tools, from classic cylinders to cans:.
到不知道从哪弄到的大塑料袋，封闭自己：。
Seal yourself up in a big plastic bag you don't know where you got it.
如果被来往的车辆剐蹭到，还会有一定的交通危险。
If be scraped by traffic vehicle rub, still can have certain traffic danger.
从远处看上去，他们俨然已经与世隔绝，形成了一道看起来无懈可击的空气魔法盾。
Seen from a distance, they were isolated, forming a seemingly impeccable air shield.
如果不考虑持续发展因素，这套生态循环系统的闭环，还能让人嗅出几分朋克的味道。
The closed loop of the eco-circulation system can also give a sense of punk if you don't take into account sustainable development.
。
.
夸张是夸张了点，只要自己不憋，自然是无可厚非。
Hyperbole is a little exaggeration, as long as you do not hold, naturally is justifiable.
。
.
只是，这种“闭环生态”固然不会受到外界空气影响，但对于个人的交通出行安全来说，显然会给自己和他人造成更多不必要的麻烦。
However, this kind of "closed-loop ecology" will not be affected by the outside air, but for the safety of personal traffic, will obviously cause himself and others more unnecessary trouble.
。
.
所以，不管是民间打什么多么想秀出自己的聪明才智，在冷酷的新型肺炎疫情面前，还是希望在尽可能科学的情况下进行防护。
So, no matter how smart the people are, they want to protect themselves against the cold new pneumonia as scientifically as possible.
。
.
既不要过分紧张，也不必寄希望于自己的“土制口罩”能给到靠谱的保护。
Neither over-stress nor hope that your "earthen mask" will provide reliable protection.
当下最安全的防护措施，依然是减少出行的次数；必须要出门的情况下，也请务必要戴好正规的口罩，进行科学合理的防护。
The safest protection is still to reduce the number of trips. If you have to go out, be sure to wear a proper mask for scientific and reasonable protection.
。
.
可莫要因为自己一时的“小聪明”招来潜藏的“大麻烦”了。
But don't let your momentary "little cleverness" cause potential "big trouble."
。
.
※文中涉及案例均为“反面教材”，切勿模仿。
vt. no, not, never, never, seldom, little, little, hardly, little, little, little, little
特殊时期，请大家不要存在侥幸心理，出门一定要规范佩戴口罩。
Special period, please do not exist lucky psychology, go out must standardize wearing masks.
。
